Look out!

526
00:33:22.600 --> 00:33:23.720
(BOBBLE YELLS)

527
00:33:24.400 --> 00:33:25.840
Man overboard!

528
00:33:29.440 --> 00:33:31.520
Hard to port! Hard to port!

529
00:33:33.120 --> 00:33:35.360
Turn the boat!
Turn the boat!

530
00:33:38.440 --> 00:33:40.840
Guys! We're running
out of river!

531
00:33:42.720 --> 00:33:45.560
That's all right,
