need's a little.

532
00:33:45.640 --> 00:33:47.160
Rosetta, come grab my feet.

533
00:33:47.200 --> 00:33:48.280
What?

534
00:33:52.360 --> 00:33:55.040
Hang on!
We're going straight down!

535
00:33:56.720 --> 00:33:57.800
Oh, no!

536
00:33:59.480 --> 00:34:00.800
(ALL SCREAMING)

537
00:34:00.880 --> 00:34:02.480
